{"tid":83562,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人會突然冇原因咁想喊？","createTime":"2017-01-16T22:42:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T18:26:56.000Z","uid":16068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"70131f897886fd2d695ddaab4a9a812a3dcdf3e8","tid":83562,"uid":16068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T22:42:27.000Z","msg":"唔知點解成日一個人就會突然想喊<br />\n冇發生咩事<br />\n同人傾傾下計 睇下故 睇下youtube 上下連登 打下機<br />\n只要係自己一個人個陣就會突然間想喊<br />\n<br />\n係完全冇原因<br />\n就算係睇緊笑片笑故 都可以突然個身抽一抽蓄就想喊 但又唔係真係大喊流好多眼淚咁<br />\n有時會係抽蓄想喊 有時甚至會流下眼淚咁<br />\n<br />\n我唔知我係咪有精神病，精神問題定點<br />\n曾經有過抑鬱<br />\n<br />\n所以想知有冇其他人同我一樣係咁？<br />\n或者有冇醫科巴打知？"},{"pid":"3f1f152b32a04b07d29f05cf213691f003afffe5","tid":83562,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T22:49:41.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"a517a1128c98ea27ee6fdeb4bab463c4804cf328","tid":83562,"uid":42044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T23:07:17.000Z","msg":"鬼上身"},{"pid":"74bb1b8758cdf37b79ad1390830956dd20e5107f","tid":83562,"uid":57607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T23:08:58.000Z","msg":"因為空虛同寂寞<br />\n有時同一班朋友都會有種孤獨感覺<br />\n覺得個群體唔屬於自己<br />\n<br />\n解決方法係享受當下，你自己食飯只有你自己飽，食飽啲享受下啲味道啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d77d6c6bbe8d9e187507de7cd20e90fa4198fc","tid":83562,"uid":32973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T23:09:36.000Z","msg":"我都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09743739c158f54b595ed42f35fb7f2122f312d9","tid":83562,"uid":39338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T23:12:59.000Z","msg":"你喊乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c8deb092c55b58a853d5d0a9c4aca21c094ffc","tid":83562,"uid":70811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T00:43:33.000Z","msg":"我試過毫無原因地好唔開心，呢個情況最可怕，因為無原因，所以解決唔到，亦無從向人傾訴"},{"pid"